Title: S27:E6 - The Crossover of Health, Technology and Art (Daniel Bourke)
Description: Meet Daniel Bourke, Founder of mrdbourke Studios and Founder of Nutrify. Daniel shares his experiences trying to learn to code four different times before it finally stuck, how he’s combining his passions for health, technology and art and the time he built his own machine learning roadmap.
